name: JAX01.WAD
description: This is Wad is a straight-forward you-against-them commando sort of thing. This wad is fast action and it will take speed and intelligence to complete it... ...well, maybe just speed. A friend and I tried a co-op mode and it did run a little slow because the amount of creatures that are present... and we were using 486/66 computers with 14.4 baud modems to play.
